full_summary:
# Public Works and Government Services Canada

## Tender Notice

**Notice Title (Title and French Title)**: Fresh Fruit and Vegetables 

*   **Solicitation Number (Numero de Soumission)**: 21501-215455/D 
*   **Amendment Number (Numero de Modification)**: 1 

### Solicitation Details

**Notice Type**: Request for Proposal 
**Procurement Method**: Competitive - Open Bidding 
**Procurement Category**: Goods and Services 
**Trade Agreements**: World Trade Organization Agreement on Government Procurement (WTO GPA) 
Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership (CPTPP) 
Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA) 
Canada-UK Trade Continuity Agreement (Canada-UK TCA) 
Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA) 
Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement 
Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement 
Canada-European Union Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement (CETA) 
Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (CPFTA) 

### Contract Details

**Reference Number**: PW-STN-201-5583 
**Tender Status**: Expired 
**Expected Contract Start Date**: None 
**Expected Contract End Date**: None 
**Regions of Delivery**: 
*   Manitoba 
*   Alberta 
*   Saskatchewan 

### Tender Description

**Background**: 
The Correctional Service of Canada requires a contract for the supply and delivery of fresh produce on an as-and-when-ordered basis. 
The contract covers geographical zones, and the delivery dates are mentioned above.
 
In case a supplier is successful in more than one zone, the awards will be combined for that supplier. In all other cases, one Standing Offer will be issued for each zone for the six-month period. 

### Contact Information

**Contact Person**: 
Rina Marsland 
PWGSC Contact Phone: (306) 241-5742 
Fax: (418) 566-6167 
Email: rina.marsland@pwgsc-tpsgc.gc.ca 

## Additional Information

### Contract Documents

The solicitation documents can be found on the Public Services and Procurement Canada, Bid Shopping and ePortal Website:
https://canadabuys.canada.ca/documents/pub/att/2022/09/07/61e99a494d2df1bacdd0f293565f29be/solicitation_d_annex_b_bilingual_21501-215455_produce_-_regional.xlsx,https
